'''洛杉矶第一公理会教堂'''（First Congregational Church of Los Angeles）是一个历史性的[[公理会|公理会]]教堂，在美国加州洛杉矶南联邦大道540号。

该堂创建于1867年，是该市最古老的连续使用的新教堂会。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Richardson|first1=Eric|title=Downtown's Churches: First Congregational|url=http://blogdowntown.com/2008/07/3449-downtowns-churches-first-congregational|accessdate=2 August 2016|date=11 July 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216103633/http://blogdowntown.com/2008/07/3449-downtowns-churches-first-congregational|archive-date=2017-02-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
目前的教堂建于1932年，是一座令人印象深刻的英国哥特复兴建筑，由洛杉矶建筑师Allison＆Allison设计，巨大的混凝土结构用超过500吨的钢筋加固。其主塔高157英尺，重30000吨。

该堂拥有世界第二大管风琴。

2002年3月15日，该堂被洛杉矶文化遗产委员会指定为洛杉矶历史文化古迹<ref>{{cite web|author1=Los Angeles Department of City Planning|title=Historic-Cultural Monument (HCM) List|url=http://preservation.lacity.org/commission/designated-historic-cultural-monuments|website=Office of Historic Resources|publisher=City of Los Angeles|accessdate=2 August 2016|page=26|archive-date=2019-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813231726/https://preservation.lacity.org/commission/designated-historic-cultural-monuments|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该堂一直是拍摄广告，电影，音乐视频和电视节目的热门地点。<ref>{{cite web|author1=Lindsay|title=The First Congregational Church of Los Angeles from "My So-Called Life"|url=http://www.iamnotastalker.com/2010/12/23/the-first-congregational-church-of-los-angeles-from-my-so-called-life/|website=iamnotastalker.com|accessdate=2 August 2016|archive-date=2019-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219175917/http://www.iamnotastalker.com/2010/12/23/the-first-congregational-church-of-los-angeles-from-my-so-called-life/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Filming|url=http://www.fccla.org/filming.html|accessdate=2 August 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140914165544/http://www.fccla.org/filming.html|archivedate=14 September 2014}}</ref>

